#: ../../source/tutorial.rst:114 84d5d084e9014492bb560e84e9bf6e5c
msgid ""
"``Model.run_iteration()``: Execute one time step from the current node state"
" and return the updated node state."
msgstr "\"Model.run itration ()\" : 执行当前节点状态的一次步骤并返回更新的节点状态 。"

#: ../../source/tutorial.rst:115 c68e27ef5cff43d4a5d003e9e77cca38
msgid ""
"``Model.run_iterations(times)``: Execute multiple time steps starting from "
"the current node state and return the final node state after all iterations."
msgstr "\"Model.run itrations(时间)\": 执行从当前节点状态开始的多个时间步骤,并在所有迭代后返回最终节点状态."

#: ../../source/tutorial.rst:116 df1fca38667f4938ac245e26d8296427
msgid ""
"``Model.run_epoch(times)``: Execute multiple time steps starting from the "
"initial state and return the final node state after all iterations."
msgstr "\"Model.run epoch(时间)\": 执行从初始状态开始的多个时间步骤,并在所有迭代后返回最终节点状态."

#: ../../source/tutorial.rst:117 c8976c9a50a24e08bfb527e0f86cbc86
msgid ""
"``Model.run_epochs(epochs, times, batch_size)``: Perform multiple Monte "
"Carlo simulations in batches, each starting from the initial state, and "
"return the final node states."
msgstr "“Model.run epocts(日期、时间、批次 大小)”“: 分批进行多次蒙特卡洛模拟,每场从初始状态开始,并返回最终节点状态."

